{"title":"十年之后","authors":["路易·艾黎"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔新西兰〕路易·艾黎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十年岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万千变化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转瞬已成过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今在北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个令人追念的日子到来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们同这位挚友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心志相通的感情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又油然生起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埃德加·斯诺的工作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今仍在继续，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为他的祖国美利坚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为整个广阔世界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"增进了解和带来知识。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回顾以往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为使他的国家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和他爱慕日深的中国改善关系，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他曾作出不懈努力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的工作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为未来更美好的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奠定了牢固根基。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他和马海德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿越一道道黄土峡谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到达保安时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们有谁稍许意识到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那次西行的结果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟会影响美国的对华政策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是怎样使他们自己的思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变得开阔而深刻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在保安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他同领导人和普通战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数度长谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"史诗般的斗争"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历历呈现在他们眼前："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饥肠辘辘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣履单薄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶风冒雨爬过雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又穿过神秘莫测的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草地沼泽；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当人们读到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"《西行漫记》中栩栩如生的叙述，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们再次认识到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国拥有一代青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能够同心协力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把今天的水平全面推向新高度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从旧世界中开创新天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让高地披上绿装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让草原获得新生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼结出硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工业充分为人民大众服务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今，在1982年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们相聚在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重温昔日的记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缅怀斯诺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的著作和他的生活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他对青年的热情关切；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着时间的流逝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的形象更加高大光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，他已成为传奇式人物。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在和将来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都源于过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而他所见的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及曾经精采地描述过的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老红军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今依然在奋进不息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1982年2月于北京（吕婉如译）（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斯诺（左）、艾黎（右）和王安娜一九三八年在上海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（中国革命博物馆供稿）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}